  "remarks": "LLC “Aviation Systems and Complexes” is a Russian developer and manufacturer of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs). It manufactures the first-person view UAV “ASK X-2” used by the Russian Armed Forces. Therefore, LLC “Aviation Systems and Complexes” is forming part of Russia’s military and industrial complex.",
